      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garaged and following every service check to a T. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the showroom price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
